Mplus Print Model Modification Indices

Source: R/mplus_print.R
mplus.print.model.modification.indices.Rd

Show the model modification indices

Usage

mplus.print.model.modification.indices(file, getdf = FALSE)

Arguments

file

the quoted name of an existing H5 file

getdf

logical

Value

A data frame containing the modification indices

Examples


ex5_5_wlsmv <- system.file("extdata", "ex5_5_wlsmv.h5", package = "mplush5")
mi <- mplus.print.model.modification.indices(ex5_5_wlsmv)
#> Model Modification Indices:  Minimum value = 10.000000
